review 1: We like their bistro and bakery at this place. They have Chinese style food and they are freshly made in the kitchen. Their bakery side on the ground floor also really good with reasonable prices. They have another location with their bakery near the market nearby.
review 2: The food and also the cake & doughnut was so good, for me this is the best in town. The place so aesthetic, but unfortunately the air circulation is so bad, they don‚Äôt have a fan or AC.
review 3: We keep coming back again and again for delicious food. I would give even 6 stars if they'll sell beer and wine.
review 4: Nice place to hang out. But the price is $$$. Highly recommend for couples.
review 5: Local pioneer for good place to hangout, unfortunately not so much for the cakes and the menus. Good interior. Limited parking space.
